articles.description: Sterling Taplin scored a career-high 30 points and Tulsa beat UConn 73-71, sweeping the season series from the Huskies.
articles.headline: Taplin scores 30 to lead Tulsa to a 73-71 win over UConn

articles.description: Darnell Edge hit the second of two free throws with 13 seconds left to give Fairleigh Dickinson an 80-79 win over Mount St. Mary's in a Northeast Conference battle Thursday night.
articles.headline: Fairleigh Dickinson knocks off Mount St. Mary's, 80-79

articles.description: With 2.9 seconds on the clock Josh Reaves delivers a baseball pass to Tony Carr who finishes a tough layup and draws the foul.
articles.headline: Carr puts exclamation point on first half with and-1 bucket

articles.description: Cougars' guard Armoni Brooks knocks down a clutch trey to put the Cougars up by 5 with two minutes remaining.
articles.headline: Houston's Brooks drills the dagger 3-pointer

articles.description: JoJo Cooper scored 23 points with seven rebounds and six assists and Wagner defeated Sacred Heart 99-84 on Thursday night to clinch at least a share of the Northeast Conference title.
articles.headline: Wagner clinches at least share of NEC title with 99-84 win

articles.description: Wajid Aminu scored a career-high 29 points and Ivan Gandia-Rosa dished out a career-high 18 assists as North Florida came back to beat SC Upstate 109-100 on Thursday night.
articles.headline: Aminu, Gandia-Rosa lead high-flying Ospreys to victory
